# Git LFS configuration for large firmware files
# Uncomment the line below if you want to use Git LFS for .bin files

# *.bin filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text

# To enable Git LFS:
# 1. Install Git LFS: https://git-lfs.github.com/
# 2. Run: git lfs install
# 3. Uncomment the line above
# 4. Run: git lfs track "*.bin"
# 5. Commit .gitattributes: git add .gitattributes && git commit -m "Enable Git LFS"
